{"tid":1267163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「身體力行」擺坐有貼嘅！ - 的士總會抗議稱「太多暴動」致生意大跌 千輛的士貼口號撐林鄭","createTime":"2019-06-29T18:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T06:37:26.000Z","uid":47414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc24e083c9fc26c35e9bec8230db9d694d76d57","tid":1267163,"uid":47414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"各位司機，想更好生意，記得貼！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190629/59770823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59770823&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=892b9596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59770823&h=15c1aa82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190629/59770823</a><br />\n<br />\n香港的士司機從業員總會成員今午在中環天星碼頭請願，以「保法制 保安定 保飯碗」為題，支持行政長官林鄭月娥依法施政，又希望廣大市民理性和平表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n該會的財務總監王宣麗表示，總會約有5萬多名會員。直到7月1日，總會內有1,000部的士都會貼上口號，以表對政府施政的支持。她續指最近「太多暴動」，所以決定走出來告訴香港市民，現時的士司機的生活好艱難，「啲青少年朋友搞太多活動，封咗好多路」，從而影響司機生計，其中90%市區的士受影響，而全港則估計有萬多部的士受示威影響。"},{"pid":"8983093796d0eb314de9d84c334ce90d11d19e08","tid":1267163,"uid":5680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19j7Fir.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19j7Fir.gif&h=c47c7b96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ce6f5335a27ae0a30b962ca1ca472862c757899","tid":1267163,"uid":34342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:08:57.000Z","msg":"以後坐uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920489778d37b361740b70a2456a3238f726e3de","tid":1267163,"uid":32505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:10:29.000Z","msg":"的士佬真係的士佬<br />\n咩係暴動都分唔清<br />\n亂鳩咁up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f790d8e4dd5c6047db24590f0618b7c1881523","tid":1267163,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:10:41.000Z","msg":"記得貼<br />\n<br />\n違泊要打咩電話呢"},{"pid":"8572096e0ab5f2f27e90ce1a45e344d257f07b20","tid":1267163,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"又被代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9sxa8A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9sxa8A.png&h=9a4d1298&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Op0e8Vh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOp0e8Vh.png&h=c932ce05&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}